        {
          "img": "https://scontent.fomr1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68969898_2525910027430632_846626203950383104_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&_nc_ohc=EnOiSUncYbMAX83Ckke&_nc_ht=scontent.fomr1-1.fna&oh=55df342ba6085a7124965b111270193c&oe=5EFE1D9F",
          "title": "<i class=\"fab fa-facebook\"></i> Anca Blaga",
          "text": "\"Amazing place to feel the cultural heritage of Rosia Montana. We stayed in Book Room - the old bank from Rosia, where miners came to exchange the gold for money and explosives.\nGreat start-point for visiting the area. Thank you Adi and Iulia for a great stay, for the movie about Rosia and for the amazing sunset from the church tower. PS: We hope the cats recovered after our kids stressed them for 4 days.\"",
          "link": "https://www.facebook.com/pg/casapetrirosiamontana/reviews"
        },
        {
          "img": "https://scontent.fomr1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/58682383_2246764692213832_995417378755969024_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&_nc_ohc=SE7ac4_f7rYAX9HgWzb&_nc_ht=scontent.fomr1-1.fna&oh=06c88ee5933ae4de15eae231f6fe8cec&oe=5EF8C5AA",
          "title": "<i class=\"fab fa-facebook\"></i> Florin Matieş",
          "text": "\"O locație deosebita care te duce înapoi în timp, gazde minunate, primitoare, de nota 10.Aici găsești tot ce ai nevoie, pe lângă liniște și relaxare, biciclete, ghizi, chiar proprietarul ne-a făcut într-o seară o prezentare cu poze și filmulețe a istoriei Roșii Montane. Recomand cu încredere, dar cel mai sigur, haideți și vedeți cu ochii voștri.\"",
          "link": "https://www.facebook.com/pg/casapetrirosiamontana/reviews"
        },
        {
          "title": "<i class=\"fab fa-tripadvisor\"></i> Ramona Vesa",
          "text": "\"If you are looking for a special location, nature, history, good local food this is a place to be. Not a luxury location for sure but an old romanian house very nice arranged for guests. The host is friendly, a lot of outdoor activities, guided montain trips , visiting old gold mines. The food was prepared by the neighbours, really tasty\"",
          "link": "https://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g9998203-d9871602-Reviews-Casa_Petri_Rosia_Montana-Rosia_Montana_Alba_County_Central_Romania_Transylvania.html",
          "img": "https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/77/d6/ed/20200101-142425-largejpg.jpg"
        },
        {
          "title": "<i class=\"fab fa-google\"></i> Adrian Vlad",
          "text": "\"Passionate host and great location. The house is situated in the middle of the historical part of the village, with a shop 2 minutes away where you can shop for food, water and other supplies. The host was kind enough to take us on tours around the village and even on a MTB trip 50 km long, up until to Geamana village, through beautiful landscapes.\"",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/travel/hotels/entity/CgsIjMbBg5X14LfHARAB/reviews?g2lb=2502548%2C4254308%2C4258168%2C4260007%2C4270442%2C4274032%2C4291318%2C4305595%2C4306835%2C4308216%2C4314846%2C4317915%2C4328159%2C4329288%2C4330113%2C4346235%2C4347918%2C4348884%2C4270859%2C4284970%2C4291517%2C4292955%2C4316256&hl=en&gl=ro&un=1&rp=EIzGwYOV9eC3xwE4AkAASAE&ictx=1&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj2j4W5sdfnAhWLw4sKHe4cAQIQ4gkwDnoECAsQBA&hrf=IgNST04qFgoHCOQPEAIYFxIHCOQPEAIYGRgCKACCASUweDQ3NGVjY2UwNDZjOTlkNDE6MHhjNzZmODNhOTUwNzA2MzBjmgEnGiUweDQ3NGVjY2UwNDZjOTlkNDE6MHhjNzZmODNhOTUwNzA2MzBj",
